<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>แบบฟอร์มเก็บข้อมูล</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
}

body{
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#fff9c4,#ffe082);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}

.container{
    background:#fff;
    width:380px;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}

h2{
    text-align:center;
    color:#d4a017;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

label{
    display:block;
    margin-top:12px;
    margin-bottom:5px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

input, select{
    width:100%;
    padding:10px;
    border:2px solid #fdd835;
    border-radius:10px;
    outline:none;
}

input:focus, select:focus{
    border-color:#fbc02d;
}

button{
    width:100%;
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:12px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:#fbc02d;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
    background:#f9a825;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <h2>แบบฟอร์มเก็บข้อมูล</h2>

    <form>
        <label>ชื่อ-นามสกุล</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="กรอกชื่อ">

        <label>อายุ</label>
        <input type="number" placeholder="กรอกอายุ">

        <label>เพศ</label>
        <select>
            <option>ชาย</option>
            <option>หญิง</option>
            <option>ไม่ระบุ</option>
        </select>

        <button type="submit">บันทึกข้อมูล</button>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
